[draft] The wearer gains immunity to effects depending on the number of stacks of the {g|Encyclopedia:UnyieldingBeacon}Unyielding Beacon{/g}:
6 and more stacks — immunity to {g|Encyclopedia:BleedingEffect}bleeding{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:CommonStatuses}effect{/g};
9 and more stacks — immunity to {g|Encyclopedia:ToxinEffect}toxin{/g} effect;
12 and more stacks — immunity to {g|Encyclopedia:BurningEffect}burning{/g} effect;
